wal amount?\",\"answer\":[\"Payouts are calculated based on the payment model, the quantity and quality of attracted traffic confirmed by the advertiser, and the terms of a specific offer.\",[\"$\",\"br\",null,{}],\"The minimum withdrawal amount is $100.\"]},{\"question\":\"How often will I receive payments?\",\"answer\":\"Payments are made twice a week - on Mondays and Fridays, to any convenient payment method presented on the platform.\"},{\"question\":\"What payment methods are available?\",\"answer\":\"We offer various payment methods, including Capitalist, cryptocurrency and others. You can choose any convenient one from those presented on our platform.\"}]},{\"title\":\"General questions\",\"items\":[{\"question\":\"What are the prohibited traffic sources in OctoCPA?\",\"answer\":\"Information on accepted and prohibited traffic sources is set by the advertiser depending on the conditions of a specific offer. Fraud and motivated traffic are always prohibited. Remember, the advertiser expects to receive active, targeted traffic.\"},{\"question\":\"What are the working hours of the partner department?\",\"answer\":\"Our support and partner departments process requests from Monday to Friday from 10:00 to 19:00 Moscow time (GMT+3). During this period, we promptly respond and provide the necessary assistance. Requests received after business hours may take longer to process. In the event of force majeure, we will make every effort to resolve the issue as quickly as possible.\"},{\"question\":\"What types of offers are available in the affiliate network?\",\"answer\":\"We are one of the few CPA networks with special expertise in the Adult vertical. Our catalog contains a wide selection of adult offers covering various areas of this vertical. You will find offers with different payment models suitable for your target traffic sources, as well as working conditions that will satisfy any preferences and goals. Regardless of what you specialize in, we will always have a suitable offer for your traffic.\"},{\"question\":\"Is it possible to receive payment early?\",\"answer\":[\"Yes, this option is discussed individually with your personal manager.\",[\"$\",\"br\",null,{}],[\"$\",\"br\",null,{}],\"However, it is important to understand that early payments are possible provided the traffic quality is consistently high and volumes are large.\"]},{\"question\":\"Is it possible to increase the rate?\",\"answer\":\"We always go to meet our trusted partners who attract quality traffic. Rate increases are provided for them. High traffic volume, with high quality, is the main reason for increasing the rate.\"},{\"question\":\"What is hold?\",\"answer\":[\"Hold is a period of time during which the quality of traffic attracted by the webmaster is analyzed, as well as additional checks by the anti-fraud system. The hold period may vary depending on the terms of the offer and may be increased if fraud is suspected.\",[\"$\",\"br\",null,{}],[\"$\",\"br\",null,{}],\"Confirmed leads will be paid according to the affiliate program payment schedule.\"]},{\"question\":\"What is the difference between CPA and Revenue Share?\",\"answer\":[\"RS (Revenue Share) is a payment model in which the affiliate receives a percentage of the amount deposited or lost by the user attracted via his referral link.\",[\"$\",\"br\",null,{}],[\"$\",\"br\",null,{}],\"CPA (Cost Per Action) is a payment model in which the affiliate receives a fixed amount for the user's target action performed via his referral link.\"]},{\"question\":\"What is SOI, DOI?\",\"answer\":[\"SOI (Single Opt-In) and DOI (Double Opt-In) are models for confirming user subscriptions.\",[\"$\",\"br\",null,{}],[\"$\",\"br\",null,{}],\"SOI (Single Opt-In) — the user leaves their data, such as email or phone number, and automatically becomes a subscriber, without requiring additional confirmation.\",[\"$\",\"br\",null,{}],[\"$\",\"br\",null,{}],\"DOI (Double Opt-In) — after entering the data, the user must confirm their subscription, for example, by clicking on a link in an email. This model provides higher-quality and targeted leads, since the user confirms their desire to receive content or services with their action.\"]},{\"question\":\"What is KPI?\",\"answer\":[\"KPI (Key Performance Indicators) are the advertiser's requirements for traffic, which are used to assess its quality and payback. The conditions under which traffic will be paid are specified in each offer.\",[\"$\",\"br\",null,{}],[\"$\",\"br\",null,{}],\"Fulfillment of the established KPIs can affect the improvement of cooperation conditions, such as the size of payments, access to exclusive offers or the provision of additional bonuses.\"]},{\"question\":\"What is the test limit (Cap)?\",\"answer\":[\"When you first start working with any offer, you need to pass the qualification so that your traffic is recognized by the advertiser as high-quality. To do this, you need to bring a limited number of conversions to the offer in test mode - they are called a test limit.\",[\"$\",\"br\",null,{}],[\"$\",\"br\",null,{}],\"When the test limit is reached, you need to stop the traffic and inform your personal manager about it.\",[\"$\",\"br\",null,{}],[\"$\",\"br\",null,{}],\"If your traffic is approved, a payment will be scheduled for it in the next week. Then, after agreement with the advertiser, you can launch advertising campaigns again.\"]}]},{\"title\":\"Technical questions\",\"items\":[{\"question\":\"What should I do if I have technical problems?\",\"answer\":[\"If you have any technical issues, please contact our support team at\",\" \",[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"target\":\"_blank\",\"rel\":\"noopener\",\"href\":\"mailto:support@TrafficTrend.com\",\"children\":\"support@TrafficTrend.com\"}],\". We will promptly process your request and make every effort to resolve the issue.\"]},{\"question\":\"What is Postback?\",\"answer\":\"Postback is a URL that allows the CPA network to receive automatic notifications from the advertiser about the user performing a target action (for example, a purchase or registration). This allows you to track conversions and award partners with a reward.\"},{\"question\":\"How is my traffic and conversions tracked?\",\"answer\":\"We use modern tracking systems that allow us to accurately measure your traffic and conversions. Data update times may vary depending on the advertiser platform, all detailed information will be specified in the offer.\"}]}],\"contact\":{\"title\":[\"If you have any questions,\",[\"$\",\"br\",null,{}],\"feel free to contact us\"],\"button\":\"Contact\"}},\"reviews\":{\"title\":\"Testimonials\",\"description\":\"Opinion of our partners\"},\"about\":{\"main\":{\"title\":\"OctoCPA\",\"cardTitle\":\"About the company\",\"cardText\":[\"TrafficTrendis a new generation affiliate program for those who count money, not likes.\",[\"$\",\"br\",null,{}],[\"$\",\"br\",null,{}],\"International market, exclusive offers, generous bonuses and honest payments - we have everything for you to earn real money. We work with traffic from all over the world, speak the same language as arbitrageurs and do not waste your time on \\\"just chatting\\\". Only the result - the rest is optional.\"]},\"levels\":[{\"value\":\"150+ offers\",\"label\":\"All the top picks, all in one place.\"},{\"value\":\"5+ verticals\",\"label\":\"Key niches covered — from gambling to dating.\"},{\"value\":\"100+ GEOs\",\"label\":\"Run traffic worldwide, no limits.\"}],\"history\":{\"title\":\"History\"},\"team\":{\"title\":\"Our team\",\"people\":{\"anna\":{\"name\":\"Anna\",\"position\":\"Affiliate manager\",\"description\":\"While they are thinking, she is already three steps ahead ♟\"},\"nikolai\":{\"name\":\"Nikolai\",\"position\":\"Sales manager\",\"description\":\"If you didn't find normal offers in another affiliate network, just know that he took them first…\"},\"lana\":{\"name\":\"Lana\",\"position\":\"Head of Affiliates\",\"description\":\"She looks at you a